  lines:
  - speaker: 0
    text: "Gi\u1EA5y t\u1EDD kh\xF4ng h\u1EE3p l\u1EC7"
  - speaker: 1
    text: "Gi\u1EA5y t\u1EDD ch\u01B0a h\u1EE3p l\u1EC7 th\xEC ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA7n
      l\xE0m cho n\xF3 h\u1EE3p l\u1EC7 thui m\xF2 ><"
  - speaker: 0
    text: "\u2026c\u1EADu tho\u1EA1i c\xE1i g\xEC \u0111\u1EA5y?"
  - speaker: 1
    text: "V\u1EADy b\xE2y gi\u1EDD \u0111\u1EC3 em ph\xF9 ph\xE9p \u0111\u1EC3 cho
      th\u1EBB sinh vi\xEAn tr\u1EDF n\xEAn h\u1EE3p l\u1EC7 nh\xE9!"
  - speaker: 1
    text: Doki doki~
  - speaker: 1
    text: Fuwa fuwa~
  - speaker: 1
    text: Oishikunare~
  - speaker: 1
    text: Moe Moe Kun~ Kun kun kun~
  - speaker: 0
    text: ...
  - speaker: 0
    text: "Kh\xF4ng cho v\xE0o."
  - speaker: 1
    text: "Ehhh? Nh\u01B0ng th\u1EBB n\xE0y \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ph\xF9
      ph\xE9p r\u1ED3i m\xE0 Oniichan?"
  - speaker: 0
    text: "T\xF4i kh\xF4ng tin ph\xE9p thu\u1EADt."
  - speaker: 0
    text: " Oniichan l\xE0 \u0111\u1ED3 BAKAAA :<<"
